Subject: [PATCH] ASoC: Intel: soc-acpi: add support for MTL SDCA boards
Git-commit: b06e33aa0ad46bb1cc68c0cec61f86a183f8dd43
Patch-mainline: v6.5-rc1
References: jsc#PED-6045 jsc#PED-6036 jsc#PED-6104 jsc#PED-6114 jsc#PED-6067 jsc#PED-6123

The description and board layout is changed and different
from previous ones for CometLake and Tigerlake.

The new codec layout for MTL is:
  SDW0: RT711 Headphone
  SDW1: RT714 DMIC
  SDW2: RT1316 Speaker
  SDW3: RT1316 Speaker

The previous codec layout for CML and TGL is:
  SDW0: RT711 Headphone
  SDW1: RT1316 Speaker
  SDW2: RT1316 Speaker
  SDW3: RT714 DMIC

